@Prashant Kikani, Attached here the CSV’s. Dates are from the “Requested’ & ‘Updated’ columns.
Prompts used:
Find ticket count that were created in May - No results in default model. Wrong results in Advanced model
Calculate the ticket count requested in May - No results in default model. Wrong results in Advanced model
Find ticket count that were created between the 01-June to 30-June - This is giving correct results,
Find the tickets  created by ‘Natwest’ - For some reason unable to get any results only for Organization ‘Natwest’ but works for all other Organizations. Also we have use the Organization name with exact spacings. It works for HSBC (HQ) and not for HSBC(HQ).

Please let me know if you need anymore details.
